    "description": {
      "value": "<p>For the duration, you have advantage on all Persuasion checks directed at one creature you touch that isn't hostile towards you. When the jutsu ends the creature may realize that you used a jutsu to influence its mood if it doesn't fit your previous relationship. </p><p>A creature prone to violence might attack you if they realize this. Another creature may seek retribution in other ways (At the DM's discretion), depending on the nature of your interactions.</p>",
